    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently non-operational, making it an ideal candidate for a complete restoration project or as a comprehensive parts car. The engine requires a full rebuild and does not start, while the transmission will need a thorough inspection before returning to the road. Cosmetically, the exterior shows significant rust and several large dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears. While it is not roadworthy in its current state, it offers a solid frame for someone with the mechanical expertise to bring it back to life.",
