    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-condition masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and preserved in a state of absolute perfection, this vehicle offers a driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, every detail reflects a standard of care that is rarely seen on the market. This is more than just a car; it is an investment in quality and a testament to engineering brilliance. For the collector or the connoisseur who demands nothing less than the best, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
